20Thompson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20music%20and%20audio%20streaming%20platform%20occupies%20several%20floors%20of%20the%20World%20Trade%20Centre%20in%20New%20York.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20even%20a%20space%20to%20listen%20to%20some%20records.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226346%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dark%20green%20curved%20coach%20next%20to%20a%20rack%20full%20of%20records%20and%20a%20record%20player%20with%20large%20windows%20behind%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660467a03f923f7dab01ce88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224357%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Thompson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20some%20fun%20features%20including%20a%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20so%2090's%26quot%3B%20gaming%20room%2C%20a%20separate%20arcade%20games%20room%2C%20and%20an%20artist%20listening%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Business%20Journal%20reported%20that%20the%20office%20has%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bizjournals.com%2Fnewyork%2Fnews%2F2022%2F10%2F17%2Fspotify-new-york-city-office-cat-statues.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatues%20of%20cats%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20it%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Podcats.%26quot%3B%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMattias%20St%C3%A5lhammar%2C%20Spotify's%20senior%20director%20and%20global%20head%20of%20workplace%2C%20told%20the%20publication%20that%20the%20statues%20are%20placed%20around%20the%20building%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20its%20pet%20playlist%20and%20its%20many%20podcast%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20building%20has%20several%20podcast%20recording%20booths.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20podcast%20recording%20booth%20with%20two%20women%20seen%20chatting%20with%20headphones%20on%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660467cc3f923f7dab01cead%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224481%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Thompson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20an%20arts%20and%20crafts%20room%20and%20a%20separate%20events%20space%20for%20new%20product%20launches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20campus%20is%20spread%20out%20over%202%20million%20square%20feet.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22googleplex%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5a6759a600d0efef018b4b0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20building%20on%20the%20Google%20campus%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20Google's%20second-largest%20square%20footage%20assemblage%20of%20the%20company's%20buildings%20after%20its%20111%20Eighth%20Avenue%20building%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20which%20is%202.9%20million%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogleplex's%20architect%20Clive%20Wilkinson%20designed%20it%20after%20winning%20a%20competition%20in%202004%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kqed.org%2Fnews%2F11902511%2Fwhy-googleplex-architect-says-luxury-on-site-perks-are-dangerous%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKQED%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHe%20worked%20directly%20with%20Google%20cofounders%20Larry%20Page%20and%20Sergey%20Brin%20to%20develop%20the%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Googleplex%20campus%20is%20located%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Googleplex%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5df2e1d8fd9db2757f5bc7a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20set%20up%20bee%20hives%20around%20its%20headquarters%20in%202010%20to%20support%20the%20local%20bee%20population.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EGooglers%20also%20get%20access%20to%20fresh%20local%20honey%20and%20some%20of%20them%20even%20help%20with%20beekeeping%20and%20collecting%20honey.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20has%20a%20sand%20volleyball%20court.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sandy%20volleyball%20court%20at%20Google's%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66047eeb1caec1275a6a1abb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222441%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Sullivan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWilkinson%20told%20KQED%20in%20a%202022%20interview%20that%20some%20of%20the%20cool%20on-site%20features%20have%20made%20Googlers%20overly%20dependent%20on%20the%20firm%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bdangerous.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere's%20a%20small%20pool%20where%20Googlers%20can%20take%20a%20dip.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Google%20Mountain%20View%20pool%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F57e05e0e077dcc5e1a8b5c77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221467%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EErin%20Siegal%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Googleplex%20designer%20reportedly%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20notion%20that%20you%20can%20provide%20everything%20that%20would%20support%20a%20worker's%20life%20on%20campus%20might%20appear%20to%20be%20extremely%20generous%20and%20supportive%20%E2%80%A6%20but%20it%20also%20has%20a%20whole%20range%20of%20potentially%20negative%20impacts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EApple's%20headquarters%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20'spaceship%20campus.'%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple's%20headquarters%20in%20Cupertino%20that%20has%20a%20circular%20design%20like%20a%20spaceship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6604856c16bde8d4ead2d52f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20he