0painted%20a%20tigress%20on%20a%20bag%20for%20a%20commission.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michele%20Sobel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20considered%20painting%20her%20%26quot%3Blifelong%20passion%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20journalism%20too.%20She%20worked%20as%20a%20full-time%20and%20freelance%20news%20producer%20between%202006%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArt%20was%20prominent%20in%20her%20life%20even%20while%20working%20in%20news.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20make%20some%20extra%20money%20from%20her%20artwork%20during%20that%20time%3B%20Sobel%20said%20she%20sold%20her%20first%20painting%20over%20a%20decade%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20found%20that%20as%20I%20advanced%20in%20my%20career%2C%20which%20I%20was%20working%20in%20a%20very%20stressful%20environment%20against%20deadlines%20and%20breaking%20news%2C%20and%20venturing%20into%20the%20world%20of%20motherhood%20that%20I%20just%20was%20craving%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Sobel%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20do%20more%20of%20that.%20That%20just%20made%20me%20feel%20good.%20And%20I%20felt%20that%20the%20more%20I%20was%20creating%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20better%20focus%20at%20my%20job%20and%20also%20just%20be%20a%20better%20mom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDocumentation%20shared%20with%20BI%20showed%20that%20gross%20sales%20for%20her%20business%20has%20roughly%20doubled%20between%202022%20and%202023%20and%20that%202024%20is%20off%20to%20a%20strong%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMichele%20Sobel%20Fine%20Art%20specializes%20in%20hand%20painting%20luxury%20leather%20goods%2C%20and%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20twofold%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Sobel%20said.%20Her%20business%20includes%20both%20fulfilling%20private%20commissions%20and%20doing%20onsite%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20she%20has%20seen%20making%20money%20from%20art%20become%20more%20profitable.%20She%20noted%20her%20margins%20on%20Etsy%20%E2%80%94%20where%20she%20said%20she%20sold%20art%20prints%2C%20original%20work%2C%20and%20wearable%20art%20%E2%80%94%20were%20sometimes%20just%20a%20few%20dollars.%20However%2C%20she%20now%20typically%20charges%20between%20%24350%20to%20%242%2C500%20on%20her%20private%20commission%20work%20that%20includes%20painting%20designs%20on%20bags%20and%20other%20hand-painting%20work.%20Sobel%20said%20her%20sales%20are%20mainly%20done%20through%20Instagram%20and%20through%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.michelesobelfineart.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20got%20into%20this%20to%20make%20money.%20It%20was%20always%20just%20passion%2C%20side%20hustle%2C%20hobby%2C%26quot%3B%20Sobel%20said%20about%20selling%20art%20as%20a%20full-time%20venture.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20career%2C%20so%20I%20wasn't%20thinking%20I'm%20going%20to%20change%20careers.%20I%20just%20was%20kind%20of%20doing%20because%20I%20was%20following%20my%20passion%2C%20doing%20something%20that%20I%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bag%20with%20two%20dog%20portraits%20painted%20onto%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66057e1116bde8d4ead2f53b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESobel%20had%20painted%20dog%20portraits%20onto%20a%20bag.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michele%20Sobel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EFrom%20a%20hobby%20to%20selling%20on%20Etsy%20to%20a%20LLC%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20said%20she%20was%20working%20full-time%20as%20a%20news%20producer%20through%20most%20of%202015%20before%20working%20as%20a%20freelancer%20over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20partly%20because%20she%20needed%20work%20flexibility.%20She%20said%20freelancing%20became%20more%20sporadic%20as%20she%20focused%20more%20on%20her%20art%20side%20hustle.%20Sobel%20said%20selling%20art%20was%20a%20hobby%20until%20around%202018%20and%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20said%20she%20was%20painting%20more%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20motherhood.%20She%20said%20she%20was%20able%20to%20accomplish%20most%20of%20her%20goals%20working%20as%20a%20news%20producer%20and%20was%20ready%20to%20move%20on%20to%20a%20new%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20question%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20the%20answer%20was%20%E2%80%94%20is%20there%20something%20more%20that%20I%20could%20do%20with%20my%20art%20that%20would%20be%20fulfilling%20and%20allow%20me%20the%20flexibility%20to%20be%20available%20for%20my%20children%20and%20also%20just%20to%20fill%20my%20own%20cup%20a%20bit%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20business%20has%20transformed%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20selling%20wall%20art%20to%20personalized%20art%20gifts%20and%20then%20ultimately%20to%20finding%20my%20niche%20hand%20painting%20designer%20goods.%26quot%3B%20She%20was%20able%20to%20make%20money%20through%20art%20on%20Etsy%20before%20registering%20her%20New%20Jersey%20business%20Michele%20Sobel%20Fine%20Art%20in%202022%20and%20then%20as%20an%20LLC%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20on%20Etsy%20included%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20a%20lot%20of%20watercolors%20that%20I%20would%20turn%20into%20prints%20and%20had%20them%20printed%20on%20like%20blankets%20and%20tote%20bags%20and%20scarves%20%E2%80%94%20wearable%20art%2C%20which%20actually%20does%20translate%20into%20what%20I'm%20doing%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20thoroughly%20enjoying%20the%20type%20of%20art%20she's%20doing%20now%20%E2%80%94%20hand-painting%20designs%20on%20people's%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20think%20back%20to%20what%20I%20was%20doing%20on%20Etsy%2C%20I%20spent%20so%20many%20hours%20just%20customizing%20and%20doing%20these%20things%20on%20the%20computer%2C%20which%20is%20not%20what%20I%20loved%2C%20although%20I%20was%20happy%20doing%20it%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20actually%20creating%20and%20doing%20and%20painting%20and%20creating%20this%20truly%20original%20art%20and%20pushing%20my%20creative%20boundaries%20to%20work%20in%20different%20styles%20and%20just%20capture%20different%20types%20of%20concepts%20that%20are%20often%20one%20of%20a%20kind%20and%20never%20done%20before%20is%20what%20really%20just%20makes%20my%20heart%20so%20happy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20said%20commissions%20include%20reviving%20%26quot%3Bvintage%20or%20already%20owned%20luxury%20goods%2C%20handbags%20with%20original%20art%20that%20is%20personalized%20for%20the%20client.%26quot%3B%20She%20said%20she%20also%20paints%20on%20sneakers.%20Personalizations%20can%20include%20painting%20birthstones%20or%20someone's%20dogs%2C%20for%20instance.%20She's%20also%20painted%20flowers%2C%20letters%2C%20and%20other%20requests.%20She%20said%20she%20also%20works%20in%20different%20styles%20%E2%80%94%20from%20pop%20art%20to%20realistic%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Louis%20Vuitton%20item%20with%20a%20pink%20flower%20painted%20onto%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66057ec43f923f7dab020396%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESobel%20has%20also%20painted%20flowers%20onto%20luxury%20items.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%5CtMichele%20Sobel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20being%20able%20to%20really%20personalize%20what%20a%20client%20is%20looking%20for%20to%20make%20them%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20the%20most%20happy%2C%20confident%2C%20and%20empowered%20when%20they're%20wearing%20their%20wearable%20art%26quot%3B%20brings%20her%20the%20most%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20encourage%20my%20clients%20if%20they%20have%20a%20special%20photo%20that%20they%20have%20taken%2C%20I%20can%20actually%20paint%20from%20that%2C%20or%20if%20it's%20something%20from%20someone's%20special%20vacation%20or%20traveling%20somewhere%20that%20they%20went%20that's%20memorable%20for%20them%20or%20special%2C%20I%20love%20to%20incorporate%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20my%20clients%20to%20really%20feel%20like%20they're%20part%20of%20the%20process%20and%20because%20after%20all%2C%20I'm%20spending%20all%20this%20time%20designing%20something%20and%20painting%20it%20just%20for%20them%20to%20wear.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20said%20she%20works%20on%20one%20private%20commission%20at%20a%20time%20and%20can%20take%20hours%3B%20she%20will%20paint%20for%20six%20hours%20straight%20usually.%20This%20work%20is%20usually%20completed%20within%20two%20weeks%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20time%20prepping%20what%20she%20will%20be%20painting%20on%2C%20like%20prepping%20a%20handbag%2C%20to%20sealing%20her%20work%20with%20a%20flexible%20water%20resistant%20finish%20when%20she's%20done%20hand%20painting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20often%20will%20go%20back%20to%20work%20if%20my%20kids%20are%20sleeping%2C%20put%20in%20a%20few%20more%20hours%20just%20because%20I%20am%20so%20lucky%20to%20have%20a%20job%20that%20I%20just%20love%20what%20I'm%20doing%20and%20want%20to%20get%20back%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20she%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20her%20time%20painting%20commissions%20and%20that%20painting%20is%20a%20slow%20process%20that%20she%20enjoys%2C%20she%20said%20she%20does%20spend%20part%20of%20her%20day%20planning%20for%20events%20that%20are%20coming%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20said%20events%20can%20involve%20working%20with%20%26quot%3Bluxury%20brands%20and%20stores%20and%20companies%20to%20create%20an%20event%20experience%20where%20customers%20and%20clients%20can%20come%20in%20and%20choose%20from%20a%20menu%20of%20artwork%2C%20and%20then%20I%20will%20hand%20paint%20it%20right%20in%20front%20of%20their%20eyes%20while%20I'm%20chatting%20with%20them%20and%20they%20get%20to%20walk%20away%20and%20take%20it%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Kors%2C%20Bloomingdale's%2C%20and%20LoveShackFancy%20are%20just%20some%20of%20the%20places%20she%20has%20worked%20with.%20She%20said%20she%20has%20also%20done%20corporate%20gifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20thought%20I%20would%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20paint%20in%20this%20kind%20of%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20used%20to%20just%20paint%20for%20myself%2C%20and%20now%20I'm%20getting%20to%20paint%20for%20all%20these%20people%2C%20partner%20with%20all%20these%20amazing%20brands.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20is%20now%20able%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20dream%20of%20hand%20painting%20work%20and%20original%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20passion%20project%20for%20me.%20And%20I%20will%20say%20once%20I%20got%20going%20a%20little%20bit%2C%20I%20just%20kind%20of%20always%20have%20had%20in%20my%20head%20that%20someone%20is%20going%20to%20have%20your%20dream%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20it%20be%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20advised%20other%20people%20to%20nurture%20their%20talent%20and%20passion%20%26quot%3Beven%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20exactly%20where%20you're%20going%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bexactly%20what%20the%20path%20is%20going%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhether%20you%20want%20to%20be%20a%20business%20owner%20or%20be%20an%20entrepreneur%20or%20be%20a%20creator%2C%20once%20you%20see%20the%20path%20forward%2C%20just%20follow%20it%20with%20determination%20and%20all%20the%20passion%20that%20it%20originated%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20someone's%20going%20to%20be%20doing%20it%20at%20some%20point%2C%20and%20why%20can't%20it%20be%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20turned%20a%20side%20hustle%20into%20your%20full-time%20work%20or%20a%20hobby%20into%20a%20profitable%20business%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20to%20share%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5