tritionists%20offer%20advice%20on%20readers'%20eating%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20wants%20to%20have%20more%20energy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-exercises-build-upper-body-muscle-short-time-gym-workout-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild%20muscle%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20increase%20her%20cardio%20stamina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGina%20has%20a%20desk%20job%20but%20bikes%20to%20work%20three%20times%20a%20week%2C%20which%20is%20a%2025-minute%20round%20trip.%20Three%20or%20four%20days%20a%20week%2C%20she%20goes%20for%20a%2020%20to%2030-minute%20walk%20at%20lunchtime.%20Every%20week%2C%20she%20also%20runs%20two%20to%20four%20miles%2C%20does%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-exercises-build-lower-body-muscle-short-time-gym-workout-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elower%20body%20strength%20workout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20goes%20rock%20climbing%20for%2060%20to%2090%20minutes%20once%20or%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegistered%20nutritionist%20Charan%20Bijlani%20told%20BI%20that%20Gina%20is%20doing%20a%20great%20job%20keeping%20active%20around%20her%20desk%20job.%20However%2C%20adding%20more%20variety%20to%20her%20diet%20would%20help%20support%20her%20health%2C%20and%20she%20may%20benefit%20from%20eating%20more%20overall%2C%20Bijlani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStarting%20the%20day%20with%20protein%20helps%20build%20strength%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20breakfast%2C%20Gina%20typically%20makes%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmoothie-mistake-spiking-blood-sugar-healthy-recipes-dietitian-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmoothie%3C%2Fa%3E%20consisting%20of%20oatmeal%2C%20greens%2C%20blueberries%2C%20peanut%20butter%2C%20and%20protein%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBijlani%20said%20it's%20great%20that%20Gina%20starts%20the%20day%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-daily-diet-to-lose-body-fat-keep-muscle-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprotein%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20this%20will%20help%20her%20build%20strength%20because%20it%20helps%20muscles%20recover%20from%20workouts%2C%20while%20the%20oats%20and%20produce%20provide%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20small%20tweak%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20is%20to%20think%20what%20other%20options%20you%20could%20add%2C%26quot%3B%20Bijlani%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20could%20you%20add%20a%20different%20berry%20instead%20of%20blueberries%20to%20your%20morning%20smoothie%20sometimes%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsuming%20a%20variety%20of%20plants%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20get%20all%20the%20right%20nutrients%2C%20and%20also%20supports%20gut%20health%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ETweak%20one%20part%20of%20a%20meal%20each%20week%20to%20increase%20variety%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGina's%20go-to%20lunch%20is%20chicken%2C%20broccoli%2C%20and%20brown%20rice%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20balanced%20meal%20providing%20protein%2C%20carbs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnutrition-for-weight-loss-principles-eat-fiber-protein-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20some%20fats%20depending%20on%20how%20the%20ingredients%20are%20cooked%20or%20any%20sauce%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20again%2C%20Bijlani%20advised%20against%20getting%20stuck%20in%20a%20meal%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it's%20easy%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20same%20meals%20to%20reduce%20decision%20fatigue%20and%20make%20the%20weekly%20shop%20easier%2C%20so%20maybe%20just%20try%20changing%20one%20element%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20maybe%20this%20week%20stick%20with%20the%20rice%20and%20chicken%20and%20try%20a%20new%20veggie.%20Then%2C%20next%20week%20try%20swapping%20the%20rice%20for%20quinoa%2C%20and%20the%20week%20after%20swap%20the%20chicken%20for%20fish%20or%20tofu.%20This%20helps%20get%20some%20variety%20but%20also%20makes%20it%20much%20easier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEating%20more%20equals%20more%20energy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGina%20said%20her%20dinners%20vary%20but%20she%20often%20eats%20something%20like%20shrimp%20with%20peppers%2C%20courgette%2C%20and%20pasta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBijlani%20advised%20Gina%20to%20check%20she's%20getting%20enough%20protein%20in%20each%20meal%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ensuring%20she's%20eating%20enough%20generally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20one%20of%20your%20goals%20is%20to%20have%20more%20energy%20and%20increase%20your%20cardio%20stamina%2C%20we%20may%20need%20to%20see%20if%20the%20amount%20of%20food%20you're%20having%20is%20enough%20to%20meet%20all%20your%20physical%20demands%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EAdd%20snacks%20to%20boost%20energy%20and%20strength%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBijlani%20said%20Gina%20may%20benefit%20from%20eating%20more%20snacks%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20exercising%2C%20she%20should%20eat%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-carb-pre-workout-foods-energy-boost-exercise-sports-nutritionist-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnack%20higher%20in%20carbohydrates%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20energy%2C%20such%20as%20a%20banana%2C%20some%20dried%20fruit%2C%20rice%20cakes%2C%20crackers%2C%20a%20slice%20of%20toast%2C%20or%20an%20apple%20with%20some%20peanut%20butter%2C%20Bijlani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20be%20helpful%20to%20have%20before%20your%20runs%20(just%20make%20sure%20you%20give%20yourself%20enough%20time%20to%20digest%2C%20but%20this%20can%20look%20different%20for%20everyone)%2C%20before%20going%20rock%20climbing%2C%20and%20even%20your%20strength%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Gina%20doesn't%20eat%20a%20meal%20until%20a%20while%20after%20exercising%2C%20post-workout%20snacks%20should%20contain%20both%20protein%20and%20carbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProtein%20is%20important%20in%20replenishing%20your%20muscles%20and%20for%20recovery%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBijlani%20recommended%20Greek%20yogurt%20with%20fruit%2C%20a%20few%20hard-boiled%20eggs%2C%20a%20protein%20shake%2C%20nuts%2C%20Babybels%20or%20small%20portions%20of%20cheese%2C%20rice%20cakes%20with%20peanut%20butter%2C%20or%20vegetables%20with%20hummus%20or%20cottage%20cheese.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboost-energy-strength-stamina-eat-more-snacks-carbs-protein-nutritionist-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711792022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660585eb3f923f7dab020e1a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboost-energy-strength-stamina-eat-more-snacks-carbs-protein-nutritionist-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Having%20a%20high-carb%20snack%20before%20exercising%20will%20give%20you%20more%20energy%20to%20perform%2C%20and%20protein%20afterward%20will%20help%20build%20strength%2C%20a%20nutritionist%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rhosie%40businessinsider.com%20(Rachel%20Hosie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboost-energy-strength-stamina-eat-more-snacks-carbs-protein-nutritionist-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Saina%20Nehwal%20lashes%20out%20at%20Congress%20leader's%20'sexist%20jibe'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711791753000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108897564%2Cimgsize-26274.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Foff-the-field%2Fsaina-nehwal-lashes-out-at-congress-leaders-anti-woman-remarks%2Farticleshow%2F108897447.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Saina%20Nehwal%20criticizes%20Congress%20leader%20Shamanur%20Shivashankarappa%20for%20sexist%20remarks%20towards%20BJP%20candidate%20Gayatri%20Siddeshwara%2C%20highlighting%20societal%20misogyny.%20The%2092-year-old%20MLA%20from%20Davangere%20South%20faced%20criticism%20after%20commenting%20that%20Gayatri%2C%20wife%20of%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Siddeshwara%20GM%2C%20%26quot%3Bbelonged%20to%20the%20kitchen.%26quot%3B%20Nehwal%20took%20to%20her%20social%20media%20account%20to%20denounce%20Shivashankarappa's%20remark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oscar-Winning%20Actor%20Louis%20Gossett%20Jr%20Dies%20At%2087%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELouis%20Gossett%20Jr%2C%20who%20won%20an%20Emmy%20for%20Roots%20and%20an%20Academy%20Award%20for%20An%20Officer%20and%20a%20Gentleman%2C%20has%20passed%20away.%20He%20was%2087%2C%20as%20per%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter.%20The%20actor%20died%20at%20a%20rehabilitation%20centre%20in%20Santa%20Monica%2C%20California.%20Although%20Gossett's%20exact%20cause%20of%20death%20is%20unknown%2C%20he%20had%20recently%20battled%20respiratory%20illness%20and%20prostate%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20obtained%20by%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%2C%20his%20family%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20with%20our%20heartfelt%20regret%20to%20confirm%20our%20beloved%20father%20passed%20away%20this%20morning.%20We%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20everyone%20for%20their%20condolences%20at%20this%20time.%20Please%20respect%20the%20family's%20privacy%20during%20this%20difficult%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGossett%20was%20menacing%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20tough%20roles%2C%20most%20notably%20in%20Taylor%20Hackford's%20Officer%20and%20a%20Gentleman%20(1982)%2C%20where%20he%20played%20Gunnery%20Sgt.%20Emil%20Foley%20and%20rode%20Richard%20Gere's%20character%20mercilessly%20(but%20for%20his%20own%20good)%20at%20an%20officer%20candidate%20school%20before%20engaging%20in%20an%20unforgettable%20martial%20arts%20duel.%20Gossett%20had%20a%20sleek%2C%20bald%20pate%20and%20an%20athlete's%20physique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20the%20second%20Black%20man%20to%20win%20an%20acting%20Oscar%2C%20following%20Sidney%20Poitier%20in%201964.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20role%2C%20the%206-foot-4%20Gossett%20trained%20for%2030%20days%20at%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20Recruitment%20Division%2C%20an%20adjunct%20of%20Camp%20Pendleton%20north%20of%20San%20Diego.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20put%20myself%20through%20at%20least%20some%20degree%20of%20this%20all-encompassing%20transformation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gossett%20wrote%20in%20his%202010%20biography%2C%20An%20Actor%20and%20a%20Gentleman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGossett%20began%20his%20Hollywood%20career%20in%201959%20as%20George%20Murchison%20in%20the%20original%20Broadway%20production%20of%20Lorraine%20Hansberry's%20familial%20tragedy%20A%20Raisin%20in%20the%20Sun.%20He%20later%20co-starred%20alongside%20Poitier%20and%20Ruby%20Dee%20in%20Daniel%20Petrie's%201961%20Columbia%20film%20adaptation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20major%20taste%20of%20national%20fame%20came%20from%20his%20eloquent%20performance%20in%20the%20eight-part%20ABC%20miniseries%20Roots%2C%20where%20he%20played%20Fiddler%2C%20an%20elderly%20slave%20who%20taught%20a%20young%20Kunta%20Kinte%20(LeVar%20Burton)%20to%20speak%20English.%20Eighty-five%20per%20cent%20of%20Americans%20watched%20at%20least%20some%20of%20Roots%2C%20and%20in%20January%201977%2C%20the%20show's%20conclusion%20drew%20in%20over%20100%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20top%20African-American%20actors%20were%20asked%2C%20and%20I%20begged%20to%20be%20in%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Gossett%20once%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20got%20the%20best%20role%2C%20I%20think.%20It%20was%20wonderful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter%2C%20Gossett%20also%20starred%20in%20the%20critically%20acclaimed%20telefilm%20Sadat%20(1983)%2C%20in%20which%20he%20played%20the%20assassinated%20Egyptian%20leader%20(Sadat's%20widow%2C%20Jehan%2C%20personally%20chose%20him%20for%20the%20part)%2C%20and%20he%20portrayed%20a%20baseball%20immortal%20in%20Don't%20Look%20Back%3A%20The%20Story%20of%20Leroy%20Satchel%20Paige%20in%20a%201981%20telefilm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%2060-year-plus%20career%2C%20Gossett%20excelled%20in%20a%20number%20of%20non-stereotypical%20racial%20roles%2C%20playing%20a%20hospital%20chief%20of%20staff%20on%20the%201979%20ABC%20series%20The%20Lazarus%20Syndrome%20and%20the%20title%20character%20Gideon%20Oliver%2C%20an%20anthropology%20professor%2C%20on%20a%201989%20set%20of%20ABC%20Mystery%20Movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGossett%20was%20born%20on%20May%2027%2C%201936%2C%20in%20the%20melting%20pot%20of%20Brooklyn%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20porter%20(who%20was%20adopted%20and%20raised%20by%20an%20Italian%20family)%20and%20a%20maid.%20At%20Abraham%20Lincoln%20High%20School%2C%20he%20was%20class%20president%20and%20starred%20on%20the%20baseball%2C%20track%20and%20basketball%20teams%3B%20later%2C%20he%20would%20be%20invited%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Knicks'%20rookie%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGossett%20became%20interested%20in%20acting%20after%20missing%20one%20season%20of%20high%20school%20basketball%20due%20to%20a%20leg%20injury.%20His%20English%20instructor%20suggested%20him%20to%20the%20makers%20of%20the%201953%20Broadway%20production%20Take%20a%20Giant%20Step.%20After%20defeating%20over%20400%20other%20candidates%20to%20get%20the%20main%20part%20at%20the%20age%20of%2017%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Donaldson%20Award%20for%20best%20rookie%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGossett%20joined%20James%20Dean%20as%20a%20friend%20at%20the%20Actors%20Studio%20in%20New%20York%20after%20accepting%20a%20dramatics%20scholarship%20to%20NYU.%20He%20made%20his%20movie%20debut%20in%201957%20on%20the%20NBC%20anthology%20series%20The%20Big%20Story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201964%2C%20he%2C%20Lola%20Falana%20and%20Mae%20Barnes%20sang%20in%20the%20cast%20of%20America%2C%20Be%20Seated%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bmodern%20minstrel%20show%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20produced%20by%20Mike%20Todd%20Jr.%20and%20played%20at%20the%201964%20World's%20Fair%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20he%20co-wrote%20the%20antiwar%20song%20Handsome%20Johnny%20for%20Richie%20Havens'%20first%20album%2C%20a%20tune%20the%20folk%20legend%20performed%20as%20the%20opening%20act%20at%20Woodstock%20three%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGossett%20went%20on%20to%20play%20an%20angry%20man%20living%20in%20a%20run-down%20apartment%20building%20in%20Hal%20Ashby's%20The%20Landlord%20(1970)%2C%20a%20con%20artist%20opposite%20James%20Garner%20in%20the%20slavery-era%20Skin%20Game%20(1971)%2C%20a%20drug-dealing%20cutthroat%20in%20The%20Deep%20(1977)%2C%20a%20headmaster%20in%20Toy%20Soldiers%20(1991)%20and%20a%20down-and-out%20boxer%20in%20Diggstown%20(1992)%2C%20as%20per%20The%20Hollywood%20Reporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711791720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fh9mqish_louis-_625x300_30_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Foscar-winning-actor-louis-gossett-jr-passes-away-at-87-5339082%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20was%20the%20second%20black%20man%20to%20win%20an%20acting%20Oscar%2C%20following%20Sidney%20Poitier%20in%201964%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Foscar-winning-actor-louis-gossett-jr-passes-away-at-87-5339082%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhat%20Should%20I%20Do%26quot%3B%3A%20Badminton%20Star%20After%20Congress%20MLA's%20%26quot%3BKitchen%26quot%3B%20Re