3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bif%20you%20don't%20like%20a%20player%20and%20boo%20a%20player%2C%20why%20should%20a%20team%20come%20out%20to%20issue%20a%20clarification%3F%20We%20act%20like%20this%20has%20not%20happened%20before.%20Sachin%20played%20under%20Ganguly's%20captaincy%2C%20these%20two%20have%20both%20played%20under%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20three%20have%20played%20under%20Kumble%20and%20all%20of%20them%20have%20played%20under%20Dhoni.%20When%20they%20were%20under%20MS%2C%20these%20players%20were%20cricket%20giants.%20We%20need%20to%20get%20our%20act%20together.%20This%20is%20real%20time%20sport.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20star%20batter%20Steve%20Smith%20has%20advised%20Hardik%20Pandya%20to%20simply%20%26quot%3Bblock%20out%26quot%3B%20the%20constant%20jeers%20and%20boos%20the%20new%20Mumbai%20Indians%20skipper%20is%20receiving%20from%20spectators%20at%20the%20IPL%20so%20far%2C%20as%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Ball%20irrelevant%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI'd%20try%20and%20just%20say%2C%20to%20block%20it%20out%2C%20it's%20all%20irrelevant%2C%26quot%3B%20Smith%2C%20who%20has%20faced%20abuse%20from%20fans%20across%20the%20world%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%202018%20ball-tampering%20scandal%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20told%20ESPNcricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20one%20outside%20knows%20what%20you%20are%20going%20through.%20No%20one%20(from%20outside)%20is%20in%20that%20change%20room.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmith%2C%20who%20was%20called%20%26quot%3Bcheat%26quot%3B%20by%20fans%20during%20the%202019%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20in%20England%2C%20feels%20all%20these%20abuse%20will%20come%20as%20a%20big%20surprise%20for%20Hardik%20as%20he%20is%20getting%20it%20from%20his%20Indian%20fans%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPersonally%2C%20for%20me%2C%20it%20doesn't%20bo