e%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLast%20Attack%20On...%26quot%3B%3A%20AAP%20Announces%20Mega%20Protest%20On%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Arrest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20march%20to%20protest%20against%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Atishi%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20will%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Her%20remarks%20come%20amid%20several%20reports%20of%20a%20rift%20between%20parties%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20who%20have%20come%20together%20to%20challenge%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDIA%20alliance%20is%20one.%20When%20the%20(Arvind%20Kejriwal)%20arrest%20was%20taking%20place%2C%20big%20Congress%20leaders%20were%20present%20there.%20All%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20alliance%20had%20raised%20their%20voice%20regarding%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20is%20the%20last%20attack%20on%20the%20murder%20of%20democracy%2C%20regarding%20which%20the%20opposition%20will%20also%20raise%20its%20voice%20tomorrow%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20last%20week%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20pertains%20to%20alleged%20corruption%20and%20money%20laundering%20in%20formulating%20and%20executing%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20excise%20policy%20for%202021-22%2C%20which%20was%20later%20scrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%2C%20along%20with%20other%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20will%20come%20out%20on%20Delhi%20streets%20tomorrow%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20arrest.%C2%A0%20Top%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders%2C%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20will%20attend%20the%20'maha%20rally'%20at%20Delhi's%20Ramlila%20Maidan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20leader%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20that%20they%20expect%20a%20large%20crowd%20to%20come%20out%20tomorrow%20and%20join%20their%20protest.%20He%20claimed%20that%20ever%20since%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20arrested%20the%20popularly%20elected%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%2C%20there%20has%20been%20grave%20anger%20among%20the%20people.%20He%20said%20the%20people%20from%20every%20class%20and%20profession%2C%20students%2C%20youths%2C%20and%20members%20of%20RWAs%20are%20expected%20to%20come%20to%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711787760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F0bo21f9c_atishi_625x300_30_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-protest-live-updates-india-alliance-is-one-aap-warns-bjp-on-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-5338943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20day%20ahead%20of%20the%20mega%20march%20to%20protest%20against%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Atishi%20said%20that%20the%20Opposition%20will%20put%20up%20a%20united%20front%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-protest-live-updates-india-alliance-is-one-aap-warns-bjp-on-arvind-kejriwal-arrest-5338943%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sara%20Ali%20Khan%20requests%20privacy%20from%20paparazzi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711786746000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108895817%2Cimgsize-40494.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsara-ali-khan-requests-privacy-from-paparazzi-pleads-mat-karo%2Farticleshow%2F108895817.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108895817.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESara%20Ali%20Khan%2C%20usually%20a%20favorite%20subject%20for%20paparazzi%2C%20found%20herself%20in%20an%20unusual%20situation%20as%20she%20expressed%20her%20discomfort%20with%20being%20photographed.%20Dressed%20in%20a%20white%20crop%20top%20and%20black%20flared%20pants%2C%20the%20actress%20appeared%20visibly%20perturbed%20by%20the%20presence%20of%20photographers%20as%20she%20stepped%20out%20of%20her%20car.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BSir%20Was%20Drunk%26quot%3B%3A%20Women%20Footballers%20Allege%20Assault%20By%20Official%20In%20Goa%20Hotel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20women%20footballers%20of%20Khad%20FC%2C%20a%20Himachal%20Pradesh-based%20club%2C%20have%20brought%20some%20serious%20allegations%20against%20Deepak%20Sharma%2C%20an%20executive%20committee%20member%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Football%20Federation%20-%20the%20governing%20body%20of%20the%20sport%20in%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20the%20footballers%2C%20Sharma%20assaulted%20them%20in%20a%20hotel%20room%20during%20the%20ongoing%20Indian%20Women's%20League%202%20in%20Goa.%20The%20footballers%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20AIFF%20on%20Friday%20while%20the%20assault%20is%20said%20to%20have%20taken%20place%20at%20a%20Goa%20hotel%20room%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20footballers%2C%20Sharma%20was%20offended%20because%20they%20were%20preparing%20food%20and%20physically%20assaulted%20them.%20Sharma%20is%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Football%20Association%20and%20deputy%20chairman%20of%20the%20AIFF's%20competitions%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20footballers%20also%20alleged%20that%20Sharma%20was%20drunk%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20and%20that%20he%20was%20drinking%20in%20front%20of%20them%20while%20they%20were%20travelling%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20to%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20footballers%2C%20Palak%20Verma%20talked%20to%20NDTV%20about%20the%20incident.%20%26quot%3BThat%20day%2C%20I%20was%20injured%20and%20had%20brought%20eggs%20in%20my%20room.%20At%20around%2010%3A30-11%20pm%2C%20I%20was%20in%20the%20kitchen%20with%20another%20girl%2C%20preparing%20eggs.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20sir%20called%20us%20to%20his%20room.%20The%20other%20girl%20went%20to%20his%20room%20and%20she%20was%20asked%20about%20what%20we%20were%20doing.%20She%20told%20him%20that%20egg%20was%20being%20prepared.%20Sir%20scolded%20the%20girl%20and%20then%20called%20me%20in.%20He%20asked%20in%20a%20rude%20way%20on%20why%20I%20was%20preparing%20egg%20and%20if%20I%20was%20'special'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSir%20was%20drunk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20explained%20to%20him%20that%20food%20had%20finished%20and%20that's%20why%20I%20was%20preparing%20egg%20in%20the%20room.%20He%20was%20drunk%20that%20time.%20He%20told%20me%20to%20throw%20away%20the%20eggs.%20I%20started%20crying%20and%20came%20to%20my%20room%20and%20banged%20the%20door.%20On%20hearing%20that%2C%20sir%20rushed%20to%20the%20room%20and%20without%20knocking%20entered%20the%20room.%20He%20came%20and%20physically%20assaulted%20me.%20My%20roommate%20stopped%20him%20and%20then%20he%20went%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20that%20her%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20club%2C%20Nandita%20came%20and%20pressurised%20us.%20She%20told%20us%20that%20we%20don't%20have%20any%20sanskaar.%20We%20have%20lodged%20complaint%20with%20GFA%20and%20AIFF.%20They%20came%20for%20investigation.%20They%20told%20Sharma%20to%20give%20a%20written%20letter%20saying%2C%20we%20would%20not%20be%20harmed.%20My%20age%20is%2021%20years.%20We%20are%20being%20pressurised%20to%20take%20away%20our%20complaint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPalak%20added%20she%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20sleep%20after%20the%20incident.%20They%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20play%20also%20as%20they%20are%20not%20in%20the%20right%20mental%20frame.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20incident%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jonathan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F91375-jonathan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJonathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20D'%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sousa%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F100375-sousa-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESousa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20GFA%20vice-president%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAfter%20receiving%20the%20complaint%2C%20I%20met%20the%20parties.%20A%20report%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20AIFF%20for%20necessary%20action.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20hotel%20at%20night%20too%20and%20I%20felt%20that%20from%20the%20GFA's%20perspective%2C%20it%20was%20important%20to%20lodge%20a%20police%20complaint.%20But%20our%20role%20was%20limited%20as%20we%20are%20not%20the%20victims%20and%20can't%20file%20FIR.%20But%20we%20have%20forwarded%20the%20complaint%20of%20the%20girl%20to%20the%20police%20and%20intimated%20them%20about%20the%20incident%20to%20ensure%20safety%20of%20the%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMiss%20Valenka%20Alemao%20(head%20of%20AIFF%20women's%20football%20committee)%20also%20met%20the%20girls.%20She%20took%20the%20girls%20inside%20a%20room%20where%20no%20other%20person%20was%20present.%20We%20hope%20the%20girls%20get%20justice.%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Sharma%20has%20been%20called%20for%20questioning%20at%20the%20Mapusa%20police%20station%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20by%20Goa%20Football%20Association.%20AIFF%20is%20yet%20to%20react%20on%20the%20whole%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711786680