al%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F4D98%2Fproduction%2F_133046891_21c8db23a3afa39fe16b64a748dfbfd9bde16fb80_167_2511_14121000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68686299%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC%20boards%20a%20US%20aid%20flight%20as%20air%20drops%20increasingly%20become%20the%20last%20resort%20for%20foreign%20governments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A79%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68686299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68686299.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68686299.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Meghalaya's%202%20Seats%2C%202%20Women%20Candidates%20Face%20Multi-Cornered%20Challenge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMazel%20Ampareen%20Lyngdoh%2C%2058%2C%20once%20a%20key%20Congress%20leader%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20is%20now%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Conrad%20Sangma%20government.%20She%20is%20also%20the%20National%20People's%20Party%20(NPP)%20candidate%20for%20the%20important%20Shillong%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%20Though%20the%20BJP%20is%20supporting%20Ms%20Lyngdoh%2C%20the%20Shillong%20seat%20has%20been%20with%20the%20Congress%20for%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeghalaya%20will%20see%20a%20multi-cornered%20fight%20for%20its%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20With%2010%20candidates%20contesting%2C%20a%20lot%20is%20in%20stake%20for%20all%20the%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20not%20entered%20the%20contest%20to%20keep%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20votes%20undivided.%20Its%20key%20NPP%20that%20fielded%20women%20candidates%20for%20both%20the%20seats%20has%20the%20task%20cut%20out%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20PA%20Sangma's%20legacy.%20The%20NPP%20hopes%20to%20take%20the%20Shillong%20seat%20from%20the%20Congress%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaking%20the%20contest%20interesting%20is%20the%20challenged%20by%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20Meghalaya%2C%20a%20state%20where%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20party%20views%20as%20winnable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NPP%20has%20no%20anti-incumbency%20worries%20in%20Shillong%20since%20the%20seat%20is%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20it%20is%20the%20current%20MP%20who%20faces%20this%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NPP%20is%20much%20ahead%20in%20its%20campaign.%20We%20are%20serving%20the%20people%2C%20and%20they%20know%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Ampareeen%20Lyngdoh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20NDA's%20big%20wins%20in%202014%20and%202019%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20being%20out%20of%20power%20in%20Meghalaya%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20the%20party%20managed%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20its%20Shillong%20bastion.%20Three-time%20Shillong%20MP%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Vincent%20Pala%20is%20among%20the%20last%20few%20key%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20the%20northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20people%20know%20every%20vote%20for%20the%20NPP%20is%20a%20vote%20to%20the%20BJP.%20I%20am%20the%20politician%20in%20the%20northeast%20whom%20the%20BJP%20could%20not%20dislodge.%20So%20far%20other%20Congress%20MPs%20have%20switched%20over%20due%20to%20threats%2C%20or%20they%20were%20lured.%20They%20sent%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20after%20me%2C%20but%20I%20trust%20the%20people%20of%20Shillong%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vincent%20Pala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20300%20km%20away%20from%20Shillong%2C%20in%20the%20state's%20Garo%20Hills%20region%2C%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Conrad%20Sangma%2C%20his%20party%20has%20fielded%20another%20woman%20-%20Agatha%20Sangma%2C%2043.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister's%20sister%20and%20a%20former%20Union%20Minister%2C%20Agatha%20Sangma%20will%20contest%20from%20Tura%2C%20a%20seat%20that%20she%20holds%20at%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20constituency%20has%20been%20with%20the%20Sangmas%20since%20the%20mid-1970s.%20The%20two%20women%20candidates%20of%20the%20NPP%20for%20Shillong%20and%20Tura%20are%20asking%20for%20votes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20double-engine%20government%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Conrad%20Sangma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20election%20is%20about%20continuing%20on%20the%20part%20of%20development%2C%20and%20the%20NPP-led%20government%20has%20given%20such%20a%20wonderful%20governance%20in%20the%20past%20six%20years.%20Teams%20led%20by%20the%20NPP%20have%20been%20well%20accepted%20by%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Agatha%20Sangma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contest%20for%20the%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Christian-dominated%20Meghalaya%20is%20not%20a%20straightforward%20fight%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc.%20There%20are%20six%20candidates%20for%20Shillong%20and%20four%20for%20Tura.%20They%20include%20leaders%20of%20regional%20parties%20who%20plan%20kingmakers%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20are%20now%20trying%20their%20luck%20in%20the%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNPP%20has%20chosen%20to%20ally%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20Meghalaya%20has%20always%20voted%20against%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Congress%20is%20a%20spent%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Paul%20Lyndoh%2C%20cabinet%20minister%20and%20working%20president%20of%20United%20Democratic%20party%20(UDP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20believes%20it%20has%20a%20small%20chance%20in%20Meghalaya's%20Tura%2C%20where%20former%20minister%20Zenith%20Sangma%20has%20been%20fielded.%20Key%20TMC%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Mukul%20Sangma%20is%20campaigning%20hard%20for%20his%20younger%20brother%2C%20and%20attacking%20the%20NPP%20and%20Agatha%20Sangma%20over%20supporting%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%2