olence-after-posting-video-with-an-image-of-joe-biden-hog-tied-13104322%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdonald-trump-accused-of-inciting-political-violence-after-posting-video-with-an-image-of-joe-biden-hog-tied-13104322%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fdonald-trump-accused-of-inciting-political-violence-after-posting-video-with-an-image-of-joe-biden-hog-tied-13104322%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20To%20Hike%20Petrol%20Prices%20Again.%20This%20Is%20What%20It%20Will%20Cost%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20could%20face%20a%20fresh%20burden%20of%20inflated%20petrol%20rates%20in%20the%20upcoming%20fortnightly%20review%20of%20petroleum%20prices%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20industry%20officials%2C%20the%20price%20of%20petrol%20is%20poised%20to%20inflate%20by%20nearly%2010%20Pakistani%20Rupee%20(PKR)%20per%20litre%20due%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20international%20crude%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petrol%20price%20is%20likely%20to%20jack%20up%20to%20PKR%20289.69%20per%20litre%20in%20the%20next%20fortnightly%20review%20from%20the%20current%20PKR%20279.75%20per%20litre%2C%20as%20per%20the%20estimates%20of%20the%20oil%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20price%20of%20high-speed%20diesel%20(HSD)%20is%20estimated%20to%20decrease%20by%20PKR%201.30%20per%20litre%20to%20PKR%20284.26%20from%20the%20current%20price%20of%20PKR%20285.86%20per%20litre%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20kerosene%20is%20expected%20to%20register%20a%20minor%20decline%20of%20PKR%200.17%20per%20litre%20to%20PKR%20188.49%20per%20litre%20from%20the%20existing%20PKR%20188.66%20per%20litre.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20price%20of%20light%20diesel%20oil%20(LDO)%20is%20likely%20to%20increase%20by%20PKR%200.45%20per%20litre%20to%20PKR%20168.63%20from%20the%20existing%20PKR%20168.18%20per%20litre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20local%20price%20of%20petrol%20will%20be%20raised%20due%20to%20a%20hike%20in%20prices%20in%20the%20international%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%20%26quot%3BThe%20international%20price%20of%20petrol%20jumped%20to%20%2495%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20compared%20to%20%2490%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20first%20fortnight%20of%20March.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20massive%20change%20in%20the%20petrol%20price%20would%20come%20because%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20price%20of%20petrol%20in%20the%20global%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20due%20to%20a%20global%20decline%20in%20the%20HSD%20price%2C%20there%20would%20be%20a%20decrease%20in%20its%20price%20in%20Pakistan%20as%20well.%20The%20price%20of%20HSD%20dropped%20to%20%2498%20per%20barrel%20globally%20in%20the%20last%20weeks%20compared%20to%20%2499%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20first%2015%20days%20of%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeo%20News%20reported%20citing%20industry%20officials%2C%20that%20this%20decline%20would%20be%20translated%20into%20more%20than%20a%20one-rupee%20decrease%20in%20the%20price%20for%20domestic%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20that%20the%20local%20prices%20of%20petroleum%20products%20will%20not%20be%20impacted%20significantly%20as%20the%20exchange%20rate%20has%20almost%20remained%20stabilised%20during%20the%20last%20four%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fuel%20prices%20are%20reviewed%20every%2015%20days%20based%20on%20the%20global%20rates%20and%20exchange%20rate%20of%20the%20local%20currency.%20The%20rupee%20registered%20a%20slight%20increase%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%2C%20trading%20at%20around%20277.94%20per%20dollar%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20government%20will%20announce%20the%20final%20prices%20on%20Sunday%20(tomorrow)%20which%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20April%201%20(Monday).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petrol%20prices%20remained%20u