r%20batting.%20With%20a%20scintillating%20batting%20display%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20became%20the%20first%20team%20to%20win%20away%20from%20home%20in%20this%20IPL%20following%20their%20comprehensive%20seven-wicket%20win%20over%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20on%20Friday%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20post-match%20presentation%2C%20Faf%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20the%20wicket%20was%20very%20two-paced%2C%20you%20could%20see%20that%20when%20the%20guys%20bowled%20the%20cutters%2C%20back%20of%20a%20length%2C%20the%20guys%20really%20struggled.%20We%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20decent%20score%20knowing%20that%20it%20gets%20a%20little%20bit%20easier%20in%20the%20evening%2C%20there%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20dew%20that%20came%20in.%20Looking%20at%20the%20way%20we%20batted%20in%20the%20first%20inning%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20someone%20in%20there%2C%20Virat%20was%20struggling%20to%20hit%20the%20ball%20just%20because%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20pace%20and%20the%20surface%20was%20two-paced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20the%20team%20could%20have%20done%20different%20things%20in%20powerplay%20with%20the%20ball%2C%20the%20skipper%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20always%20know%20after%20the%20game%2C%20we%20can%20say%20perhaps%20try%20one%20or%20two%20things%20but%20the%20way%20the%20two%20of%20them%20(Sunil%20Narine%20and%20Phil%20Salt)%20were%20striking%20the%20ball%2C%20some%20really%20good%20batting%20there%2C%20they%20put%20pressure%20on%20our%20bowlers.%20They%20hit%20strong%20cricket%20shots%2C%20and%20pretty%20much%20took%20the%20game%20away.%20With%20Narine%20there%2C%20you%20cannot%20go%20to%20spin%2C%20you%20want%20to%20use%20pace%20upfront.%20That%20is%20also%20a%20really%20good%20match-up%20for%20Salt%20and%20the%20way%20he%20plays.%20They%20were%20excellent%2C%20and%20really%20broke%20the%20game%20in%20the%20first%20six%20overs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFaf%20said%20that%20the%20team%20tried%20to%20have%20spin%20options%20with%20all-rounder%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20but%20there%20was%20not%20much%20spin%20during%20the%20game%20on%20the%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20tried%20the%20spinning%20options%20with%20Maxi%2C%20the%20finger%20spinners%20seem%20to%20be%20effective%20here%2C%20but%20at%20night%20there%20was%20not%20too%20much%20spin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20medium%20pacer%20Vijaykumar%20Vyshak%2C%20Faf%20said%20that%20he%20bowled%20well%2C%20but%20has%20not%20had%20many%20opportunities%20for%20RCB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20look%20in%20the%20first%20inning%20and%20we%20thought%20about%20bringing%20in%20Karn%20Sharma%20(the%20spinner).%20But%20we%20felt%20someone%20who%20could%20bowl%20really%20good%20slower%20balls%20was%20probably%20the%20most%20difficult%20bowler%20to%20face%20on%20this%20pitch.%20Dre%20Russ%20probably%20bowled%2080%20per%20cent%20of%20his%20balls%20as%20cutters.%20We%20took%20some%20lessons%20from%20that%20and%20he%20was%20the%20best%20bowler%20of%20the%20evening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20KKR%20won%20the%20toss%2C%20they%20opted%20to%20field.%20After%20losing%20skipper%20Faf%20early%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20had%20a%2065-run%20partnership%20with%20Cameron%20Green%20(33%20in%2021%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20a%2042-run%20stand%20with%20Glenn%20Maxwell%20(28%20in%2019%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six).%20Virat%20scored%2083%20not%20out%20in%2059%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20four%20sixes%20and%20took%20RCB%20to%20182%2F6%20along%20with%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20(20*%20in%20eight%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20sixes)%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndre%20Russell%20(2%2F29)%20and%20Harshit%20Rana%20(2%2F39)%20were%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20KKR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20chase%2C%20Phil%20Salt%20(30%20in%2020%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20and%20Sunil%20Narine%20(47%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20five%20sixes)%20put%20KKR%20to%20a%20fine%20start%20with%20a%20quickfire%2086-run%20stand%20in%2039%20balls.%20After%20Vyshak%20and%20Mayank%20Dagar%20(1%2F23%20each)%20dismissed%20the%20openers%2C%20Venkatesh%20Iyer%20(50*%20in%2030%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20four%20sixes)%20and%20skipper%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20(39%20in%2024%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20guided%20KKR%20to%20a%20seven-wicket%20win%20with%2019%20balls%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20won%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20on%20his%20500th%20match%20for%20his%20knock%20of%2047%20and%20one%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB%20is%20sixth%20in%20the%20points%20table%20with%20a%20win%20and%20two%20losses.%20They%20have%20just%20two%20points.%20KKR%20is%20at%20second%20with%20two%20wins%20in%20two%20games%20and%20four%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711779300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F8vcea34g_virat-kohli-rcb-bcci_625x300_30_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-was-struggling-to-rcb-captain-faf-du-plessis-pitch-talk-after-loss-to-kkr-in-ipl-2024-match-5337597%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20scored%2083%20not%20out%20in%2059%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries%20and%20four%20sixes%20and%20took%20RCB%20to%20182%2F6.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Girl's%20death%20sparks%20deadly%20mob%20violence%20in%20Mexico%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711779225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F