%3Cp%3EModi's%20popularity%20ratings%20have%20changed%20in%20cycles.%20They%20jumped%20from%20around%2040%25%20in%20February%202016%20to%2065%25%20in%20January%202017%20(just%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-on-notes-ban-to-ani-it-wasnt-a-jhatka-had-warned-people-a-year-before-1971011%5C%22%3Edemonetisation%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20then%20fell%20to%2046%25%20just%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbalakot-air-strike-what-unreleased-satellite-images-of-the-balakot-air-strikes-show-2006941%5C%22%3EBalakot%20airstrikes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20before%20reaching%2066%25%20again%20in%202020%20post%20his%20emphatic%20win%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20just%20before%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbalakot-air-strike-what-unreleased-satellite-images-of-the-balakot-air-strikes-show-2006941%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20COVID-19%2C%20Modi's%20ratings%20plummeted%20to%2024%25.%20But%20steps%20like%20100%25%20vaccination%20through%20indigenously%20developed%20vaccines%20firmed%20up%20his%20credentials%2C%20and%20his%20approval%20record%20jumped%20to%20over%2050%25%20again%20in%20January%202022%2C%20and%20was%20touching%2055%25%20by%20January%202024%2C%20which%20was%20soon%20after%20the%20G-20%20event%20in%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20debate%20about%20whether%20Brand%20Modi%20has%20peaked%2C%20whether%20there%20is%20still%20some%20room%20for%20growth%2C%20or%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20whether%20it's%20on%20a%20decline.%20There%20are%20four%20stages%20in%20a%20product%20-%20or%20brand's%20-%20life%20cycle%3A%20introduction%2C%20growth%2C%20maturity%20and%20decline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EVotes%20And%20The%20Modi%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20one%20out%20of%20every%20three%20voters%20(32%25)%20who%20voted%20for%20the%20BJP%20would%20not%20have%20done%20so%20if%20Modi%20were%20not%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20face%20of%20the%20party%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies'%20(CSDS)%20National%20Election%20Study%20(NES).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA%20received%2027.5%20crore%20votes%20in%202019%2C%20a%20lead%20of%2011%20crore%20over%20the%20the%20UPA's%2016.5%20crore%20votes.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%208.5%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20almost%2080%25%20of%20the%20lead%20margin%2C%20was%20on%20account%20of%20the%20'Modi%20factor'.%20The%20MOTN%20survey%20in%20August%202023%20showed%20that%20the%20share%20of%20voters%20who%20supported%20the%20BJP%20primarily%20because%20of%20Modi%20has%20increased%20from%2032%25%20to%2044%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20Brand%2C%20it%20seems%2C%20is%20still%20going%20strong%20and%20may%20be%20in%20a%20growth%20stage%2C%20which%20just%20precedes%20maturity.%20Opposition%20parties%20are%20hoping%20that%20this%20election%20will%20see%20his%20popularity%20peaking%2C%20and%20that%20by%202029%2C%20Brand%20Modi%20will%20start%20fading%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pillars%20Of%20'Brand%20Modi'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20image%20is%20built%20on%20three%20key%20perceptions%3A%20trust%2C%20good%20intent%20and%20delivery.%20He%20has%20been%20able%20to%20touch%20the%20hearts%20of%20people%20through%20many%20of%20his%20landmark%20schemes%20and%20their%20implementation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20similar%20views.%20While%20author%20Santosh%20Desai%20opines%20that%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Brand%20Modi%20lies%20%26quot%3Bstrength%20and%20clarity%26quot%3B%2C%20Dilip%20Cherian%20a%20renowned%20communications%20consultant%20and%20political%20campaign%20advisor%2C%20believes%20that%20'Brand%20Modi'%20works%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bsound%2C%20corporate%26quot%3B%20principle%20of%20%26quot%3Brepeat%2C%20rinse%2C%20repeat%26quot%3B.%20The%20director%20of%20Axis%20My%20India%2C%20Pradeep%20Gupta%2C%20says%20what%20PM%20Modi%20has%20is%20%26quot%3Bintent%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bone-point%20agenda%20on%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%20and%20countrymen%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20for%20Creativeland%20Asia%20Network%20founder%20Sajan%20Raj%20Kurup%2C%20the%20brand's%20success%20is%20because%20Modi%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20voters%20engaged%20through%20both%20adverse%20and%20interesting%20times%2C%20and%20even%20through%20things%20that%20are%20irrelevant%20to%20you%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20managed%20to%20win%20the%20support%20of%20women%2C%20too%2C%20who%20are%20optimistic%20about%20their%20'achche%20din'%20(good%20days)%20that%20have%20arrived%20in%20the%20form%20of%20LPG%20cylinders%20under%20the%20PM%20Ujjwala%20Yojana.%20Apart%20from%20that%2C%20there%20is%20the%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%20for%20houses%2C%20Jan%20Ausadhi%20Kendras%20for%20affordable%20medicines%2C%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20schemes%20to%20eliminate%20middlemen%20and%20leakages%2C%20and%20Jan%20Dhan%20accounts%20to%20improve%20financial%20inclusion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20He%20Remains%20Popular%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Modi%2C%20being%20popular%20in%20his%2010th%20year%20as%20PM%20is%20not%20easy.%20It%20requires%20continuous%20engagement%20with%20the%20people%2C%20consistent%20reinvention%20of%20his%20image%2C%20and%20the%20addition%20of%20new%20vote%20blocks.%20Modi%20also%20displays%20an%20uncanny%20ability%20to%20ride%20out%20public%20discontent%20over%20decisions%20that%20do%20not%20pan%20out%20the%20way%20he%20wants.%20Demonetisation%20is%20an%20example.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20implemented%20several%20schemes%20for%20almost%20all%20categories%20of%20voters%20-%20namely%2C%20youth%2C%20farmers%2C%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20seniors.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20has%20delivered%20on%20its%20ideological%20promises%20and%20provided%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20business%20through%20structural%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrand%20Modi%20towers%20over%20even%20the%20BJP's%20name%20and%20symbol%20today.%20The%20BJP's%20theme%20and%20slogan%20for%20this%20election%20is%20%26quot%3BOnce%20again%20Modi%26quot%3B%3B%20the%20political%20messaging%20is%20about%20%26quot%3BModi%20ki%20Guarantee%26quot%3B%20(Modi's%20guarantees)%2C%20rather%20than%20%26quot%3BBJP%20ki%20Guarantee%26quot%3B%20(BJP's%20guarantees).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Brand%20Modi%20that%20fetches%20the%20BJP%20additional%20votes%2C%20which%20consolidates%20voters%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20irrespective%20of%20their%20ideological%20beliefs.%20It's%20Modi's%20oratory%20skills%2C%20policies%2C%20charisma%2C%20delivery%20and%20the%20perception%20of%20India's%20raised%20global%20stature%20under%20him%20that%20have%20bolstered%20the%20party's%20winning%20prospects%20in%20elections.%20To%20sum%20up%2C%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%2C%20in%20the%20truest%20sense%2C%20Brand%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711771920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fdfa3erjg_pm-modi-rally_625x300_04_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Felections-2024-why-brand-modi-is-unlikely-to-fizzle-out-anytime-soon-5337896%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20difference%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%2C%20in%20the%20truest%20sense%2C%20Brand%20Modi.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalU