0other%20products%20at%20the%20ideal%20temperature.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%20incorporate%20natural%20preservatives%2C%20such%20as%20salt%2C%20tamarind%2C%20and%20lemon%2C%20into%20our%20recipes.%20These%20carefully%20chosen%20ingredients%20not%20only%20enhance%20flavour%20profiles%20but%20also%20contribute%20to%20prolonging%20the%20freshness%20of%20our%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Avarekalu%20uppittu%20(Rava-based%20upma%20using%20hyacinth%20beans).%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAvarakalu-Uppittu-1710946015-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345386%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAvarekalu%20uppittu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Rava-based%20%3Cem%3Eupma%20%3C%2Fem%3Eusing%20hyacinth%20beans).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20the%20magic%20of%20Sankethi%20cuisine%20to%20the%20Indian%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20inception%20%5Bof%20Adukale%5D%2C%20it%20was%20heartening%20to%20watch%20my%20parents%20and%20aunt%20bring%20in%20their%20entrepreneurial%20prowess%20and%20passion%20to%20the%20brand%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20a%20few%20years%20after%20establishing%20Adukale%2C%20demand%20for%20their%20products%20grew%20so%20extensively%20in%20Bengaluru%20through%20just%20word%20of%20mouth%20that%20they%20were%20compelled%20to%20move%20away%20from%20their%20small%2010%C3%9710%20square%20feet%20room%20in%20Malathi%E2%80%99s%20home%20to%20a%203%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%2030%20tonnes.%20In%202018%2C%20the%20venture%20shifted%20to%20an%20even%20larger%207%2C000%20sq%20ft%20facility%20in%20South%20Bengaluru%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20100%20tonnes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20capacity%20growing%20multi-fold%2C%20their%20processes%20didn%E2%80%99t%20change.%20One%20of%20the%20three%20founding%20partners%20of%20the%20business%20continued%20to%20supervise%20each%20stage%20of%20production%20to%20ensure%20product%20quality%20didn%E2%80%99t%20wane.%20What%20also%20helped%20was%20Bharat%20joining%20the%20business%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWitnessing%20great%20promise%20in%20the%20venture%2C%20I%20quit%20my%20profession%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20in%20the%20US%20to%20join%20Adukale.%20As%20someone%20passionate%20about%20food%20and%20the%20culinary%20landscape%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20bring%20in%20my%20global%20experience%20and%20innovation%20to%20scale%20the%20brand%20and%20make%20strides%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F235046%2Fbengaluru-woman-spices-entrepreneur-coffee-sambar-powder-natural-traditional-recipes-small-biz-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebringing%20regional%20food%20to%20the%20global%20map%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20an%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Old%20Bengaluru%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-and-Old-Bangalore-Launch4-1710946262-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345388%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20an%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Old%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20does%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20brand%20necessitate%20breaking%20away%20from%20your%20Sankethi%20roots%20on%20the%20odd%20occasion%3F%20Bharat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20agree%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CAdukale%20has%20always%20been%20a%20Karnataka%20brand%3B%20our%20roots%20are%20deeply%20embedded%20in%20the%20culinary%20heritage%20of%20the%20region.%20Similar%20to%20national%20brands%2C%20our%20products%20have%20their%20own%20USP%20%E2%80%94%20a%20key%20growth%20factor%20in%20the%20markets%20we%20operate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20world%20is%20our%20platter%20and%20cross-border%20integration%20of%20food%20has%20never%20been%20better.%20People%20thrive%20on%20homegrown%20recipes%20and%20products%20that%20are%20a%20window%20to%20different%20cultures.%20Given%20this%20background%2C%20our%20core%20will%20always%20remain%20the%20same.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20Adukale%20in%202017%2C%20Bharat%20became%20director%20in%202019%2C%20and%20subsequently%20the%20CEO%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Adukale%20enjoys%20an%20extensive%20selection%20of%2056%20products%2C%20available%20across%2020%20stores%20throughout%20Bengaluru%20and%20Mysuru.%20%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20established%20a%20strong%20online%20presence%2C%20ensuring%20our%20offerings%20are%20accessible%20to%20customers%20far%20and%20wide.%20As%20Adukale%20continues%20to%20grow%20and%20expand%20its%20reach%2C%20it%20remains%20rooted%20in%20its%20core%20mission%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322885%2Fkarnataka-shivaranjini-started-suggi-oota-south-indian-restaurant-in-california%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcasing%20the%20rich%20heritage%20of%20Karnataka%20cuisine%20to%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20delicious%20product%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20range%20of%20products%20currently%20comprises%20RTE%20foods%20like%20%3Cem%3Epoha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egojjavalakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Ebisi%20bele%20bath%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20spicy%2C%20rice-based%20dish)%2C%20blended%20spices%20like%3Cem%3E%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20powders%2C%20%3Cem%3Esambar%20%3C%2Fem%3Epowder%2C%20%3Cem%3Etarkaari%20gojjina%3C%2Fem%3E%20powder%20(spice%20mix%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Egojju%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enamkeens%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20savouries%20like%20%3Cem%3Enippattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(crispy%20deep%20fried%20rice%20crackers)%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekayi%20kodubale%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20popular%20deep-fried%20snack%20from%20Karnataka%20made%20using%20rice%20flour%2C%20coconut%2C%20ground%20roasted%20gram%20powder).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bharat%2C%20these%20products%20are%20free%20of%20preservatives%20and%20artificial%20colours.%20Also%2C%20with%20millets%20making%20a%20comeback%20in%20Indian%20households%20as%20superfoods%2C%20Adukale%20has%20also%20launched%20millet-based%20RTC%20products%20like%20the%20%E2%80%98Instant%20Millets%20Dose%20%5BDosa%5D%20Mix%E2%80%99%2C%20amongst%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20another%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Bengaluru.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Old-Bangalore-1710946322-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20another%20Adukale%20outlet%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EExpanding%20their%20market%20reach%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20November%202022%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EAllied%20Market%20Research%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20India%20ready-to-eat%20(RTE)%20and%20ready-to-cook%20(RTC)%20food%20market%20was%20valued%20at%20%24557.6%20million%20in%202021%2C%20and%20is%20projected%20to%20reach%20%242%2C861.3%20million%20by%202031%2C%20registering%20a%20CAGR%20of%2017.6%25%20from%202022%20to%202031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20Adukale%20compete%20with%20big%20brands%20like%20Maiya%E2%80%99s%20and%20MTR%3F%20%E2%80%9COur%20product%20range%20is%20defined%20by%20authenticity%20and%20freshness.%20While%20we%20are%20growing%20as%20a%20brand%2C%20our%20focus%20will%20remain%20on%20mastering%20traditional%20Karnataka%20food.%20This%20gives%20us%20a%20first-mover%20advantage%20in%20the%20category.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20Sankethi%20community%20has%20found%20a%20sweet%20spot%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20we%20are%20honoured%20to%20play%20a%20role%20in%20taking%20the%20Karnataka%20culinary%20legacy%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20M%20S%20Ravindra%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20great%20pride%20in%20building%20a%20community%20of%20food%20lovers%20through%20Adukale.%20Our%20focus%20on%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20quality%2C%20flavours%2C%20and%20authenticity%20has%20played%20an%20integral%20role%20in%20pivoting%20from%20a%20small%20room%20to%20a%20celebrated%20brand%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20F%26amp%3BB%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Family-Brand-Feature-Image-1711110077.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22(L-R)%20M%20S%20Ravindra%20-%20Director%2C%20Nagaratna-%20Director%2C%20Malathi%20Sharma%20-%20Director%2C%20and%20Bharat%20Kaushik%20-%20Director%20and%20CEO%20of%20Adukale.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Family-Brand-Feature-Image-1711110077.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Family-Brand-Feature-Image-1711110077-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FAdukale-Family-Brand-Feature-Image-1711110077-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com