%2C%20and%20efficient%20waste%20management.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20call%20it%20the%20king%20of%20renewable%20energy!%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreeneria%20is%20a%20testament%20effective%20to%20the%20power%20of%20perseverance%20and%20innovation%20in%20addressing%20pressing%20environmental%20issues.%20The%20company%20is%20not%20only%20contributing%20to%20a%20cleaner%2C%20more%20sustainable%20India%20but%20also%20setting%20an%20example%20for%20businesses%20worldwide%20to%20embrace%20eco-friendly%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kumar%20aptly%20puts%20it%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20simplest%20ways%20to%20express%20patriotism%20towards%20India%20is%20by%20segregating%20our%20waste.%20Adopt%20a%20two%20or%20three-bin%20system.%20Use%20one%20bin%20for%20electronic%20waste%20and%20hazardous%20materials%2C%20another%20for%20organic%20waste%20(coloured%20green)%2C%20and%20a%20third%20for%20dry%20waste%20(coloured%20blue).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20make%20sustainability%20a%20part%20of%20our%20daily%20thought%20process%20and%20actions%20for%20a%20better%20environment%20for%20our%20children%20and%20future%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20All%20photos%20courtesy%20Greeneria)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710999169000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fimage-042_11zon-1710998724.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D345419%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founder%20of%20Greeneria%20Renwable%20Technology%2C%20Bengaluru-based%20Rajendra%20Kumar%20has%20transformed%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20waste%20management%20with%20IoT-equipped%20biogas%20projects%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345419%2Fbiogas-startup-greeneria-renewable-technology-turns-wet-waste-into-fuel-for-rashtrapati-bhavan-microsoft-hp%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Holi%2C%20Play%20With%20100%25%20Edible%20%26amp%3B%20Organic%20Colours%20Handcrafted%20By%20Bhil%20Tribals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHoli%20is%20almost%20here%2C%20ready%20to%20paint%20the%20country%20with%20its%20exquisite%20hues.%20The%20exuberant%20festival%20brings%20many%20delights%20with%20it%20like%20the%20delicious%20food%2C%20drinks%20and%20traditions%20%E2%80%93%20and%20an%20underlying%20worry%20about%20the%20quality%20and%20impact%20of%20the%20colours%20used%20to%20celebrate%20the%20festival%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20synthetic%20colours%20pose%20harm%20not%20only%20to%20your%20skin%20and%20body%20but%20also%20to%20the%20environment.%20The%20chemicals%20used%20to%20prepare%20them%20can%20seep%20into%20the%20ground%2C%20pollute%20water%20sources%2C%20and%20contribute%20to%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%20problem%2C%20two%20brothers%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20who%20have%20dedicated%20close%20to%20a%20decade%20to%20natural%20conservation%2C%20came%20up%20with%20a%20solution.%20Gaurang%20and%20Saurabh%20Motta%20started%20%E2%80%98Abeer%20Holi%20Colours%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20brand%20under%20%E2%80%98Monks%20Bouffe%E2%80%99%2C%20an%20organic%20food%20and%20farming%20brand%20which%20sells%20everything%20from%20organically%20grown%20rice%2C%20maize%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277883%2Fholi-best-organic-colours-gulal-thandai-online-amazon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20Holi%20colours%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20colours%2C%20crafted%20by%20the%20Bhil%20tribe%20using%20flowers%20and%20no%20other%20additives%2C%20are%20not%20only%20natural%20but%20also%20edible!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20you%20can%20eat%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gaurang%20emphasised%20when%20I%2C%20perpl